    {
      "id": "https://boingboing.net/2026/06/09/kevin-kelly-rereads-his-big-weird-book-from-1994-and-mostly-stands-by-it.html",
      "url": "https://boingboing.net/2026/06/09/kevin-kelly-rereads-his-big-weird-book-from-1994-and-mostly-stands-by-it.html",
      "title": "[Boing Boing] Kevin Kelly rereads his big weird book from 1994 and mostly stands by it",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/ooc.jpg?fit=1200%2C1215&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/06/09/kevin-kelly-rereads-his-big-weird-book-from-1994-and-mostly-stands-by-it.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Kevin Kelly rereads his big weird book from 1994 and mostly stands by it\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"1215\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/ooc.jpg?fit=1200%2C1215&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"1200\" /></a><p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Kevin Kelly wrote <a href=\"https://geni.us/60J7\">Out of Control</a> in 1994, a sprawling study of emergence, hive minds, and bottom-up systems that arrived before the web and got mostly ignored in the US. </p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Thirty-two years later he reread it, and in a <a href=\"https://kevinkelly.substack.com/p/still-out-of-control\">new essay</a> he argues it holds up — partly because its ideas went mainstream, partly because the science barely moved. &#8212; <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/06/09/kevin-kelly-rereads-his-big-weird-book-from-1994-and-mostly-stands-by-it.html\">Read the rest </a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/06/09/kevin-kelly-rereads-his-big-weird-book-from-1994-and-mostly-stands-by-it.html\">Kevin Kelly rereads his big weird book from 1994 and mostly stands by it</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://boingboing.net\">Boing Boing</a>.</p>",
      "date_published": "2026-06-09T20:20:05+00:00",
      "authors": [
        {
          "name": "Boing Boing",
          "url": "https://boingboing.net/"
        }
      ],
      "image": "https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/ooc.jpg?fit=1200%2C1215&quality=60&ssl=1",
      "_score": 52
    },
